# Frontend UX patterns

## Single dashboard, role-gated UI

One app for admin and viewer; hide tabs/controls by role — never separate apps or URLs. Admin: 6 tabs; viewer: Overview, Forecast, History only. See feature matrix in [`docs/frontend-manual.md`](docs/frontend-manual.md).

## Navigation

- Sticky topbar: brand + live status strip + theme toggle
- Horizontal tab nav with **labels** (not icon-only); scroll-snap on mobile
- Settings: desktop sidebar from `SETTINGS_NAV` (`settings-nav.ts`); mobile category pills + subsection strip + search; **Agent access (MCP)** under System category (`system_mcp`)
- Cross-panel links via `solar-navigate-tab` custom events

## Operator safety

Kill switch and destructive actions require explicit confirmation. Unsaved-changes guard on tab leave (load shedding pattern).

## Accessibility (required for new UI)

- Tab pattern: `role="tablist/tab/tabpanel"`, `aria-selected`, `aria-controls`, `aria-labelledby`
- `:focus-visible` + `--ring`; toasts `aria-live="polite"`; validation banners `role="alert"`
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion: reduce`
- **44px min tap targets** on mobile; info tips tap-to-toggle on coarse pointers (`solar-info-tip`)

## Mobile / HA ingress

Respect `env(safe-area-inset-*)`; no double scrollbars; status pills collapse to overflow menu ≤600px. Validate against [`docs/mobile-ingress-qa.md`](docs/mobile-ingress-qa.md).

## i18n

- All user-visible strings in `frontend/src/locales/*.json`; use `t()` only
- New locale: copy `en.json` → add `LocaleMeta` + loader in `manifest.ts` → pass locale parity test (`docker compose run --rm frontend-test`)
- Send `X-Solar-Locale` on API calls; reconnect WebSocket on `solar-locale-change`
- Arabic = RTL via `dir` on `<html>`

## Boot experience

Boot splash until session resolves (`GET /api/me`); avoid blank iframe flash on HA ingress.

## Visual QA

After significant UI changes: `cd frontend && npm run docs:screenshots`; update `docs/images/frontend/` if layout changed.

## Keep this rule current

Update when you change role/tab matrix, settings nav schema, locale manifest, mobile layout breakpoints, or accessibility patterns. Full UX spec: [`docs/frontend-manual.md`](docs/frontend-manual.md).
